{"tid":1672101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T15:34:47.000Z","uid":33930,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"91007766e88ad3378fb5e83641f0ba0ca6d9e6a9","tid":1672101,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">代號：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">長龍爆買日1.0</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日期&amp;時間：</span><ins>10月26日 中午12:00</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">地點：</span><ins>全港18區黃店</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">目的：</span><ins>向支援手足嘅黃店表示感謝；鞏固黃色經濟圈</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說而家參加活動都冇人計人數，大家有冇諗過其實可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">利用hkmap.live喺全港收集數據</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n除咗可以一齊做<span style=\"color: teal;\"><ins>統計員</ins></span>之外，仲可以趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\"><ins>練習放哨報哨技術</ins></span>！同埋最最最重要嘅係可以，大家一齊挑戰黃店嘅貨存量！一齊<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>用港幣令黃店提早收檔</ins></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10.26，大家一齊召喚神獸 - 長龍</span></strong>🐉<br />\n一齊狠狠咁懲罰一啲出錢出心出力嘅黃店啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxW3aWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxW3aWG.jpg&h=1c06e3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz8dx93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz8dx93.jpg&h=10190207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK886u4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK886u4.jpg&h=f280fce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMWyx95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMWyx95.jpg&h=8ff4aead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjmVMu6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjmVMu6.jpg&h=ee11dd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43YMS96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43YMS96.jpg&h=726adbdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XW3aWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XW3aWN.jpg&h=a1e5dd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店<br />\n<br />\n上水<br />\n-孖寶Twins Bistro (提供地方/水站)<br />\n<br />\n元朗<br />\n-大阪日本料理(免費餐)<br />\n-匡樂冰室(派飯卷)<br />\n-水門泰式海南雞飯專門店(免費餐!)<br />\n-御麵(請手足食飯,幫手睇水)<br />\n-喜友此里(送野食)<br />\n<br />\n荃灣<br />\n光榮冰室(免費餐!)<br />\n<br />\n大埔<br />\n-鼎天茶室(派飯!!)<br />\n-暢和麵家(派飯!!)<br />\n<br />\n沙田<br />\n-金豆(送飲品)<br />\n-必食站(免費餐!)<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣<br />\n-元洲牛肉麵(送飲品)<br />\n<br />\n深水埗<br />\n-Caf&eacute; Sausalito(派飲品)<br />\n<br />\n石硤尾<br />\n-金沙餐廳 Sands Bakery(送蛋)<br />\n<br />\n太子<br />\n-潮州人(送飯!!)<br />\n-青花亭(免費餐!)<br />\n-coffeee Green Tea(提供地方)<br />\n<br />\n旺角<br />\n-基隆茶餐廳(派飯!!)<br />\n-叻仔記小食(送野食)<br />\n-Riders(提供地方,送飲品)<br />\n-架仔飯(提供地方,食物!!)<br />\n-清玉(送飲品)<br />\n-火之烏車仔麵之家(送飲品)<br />\n-Caf&eacute; ChocoPinky(送野食)<br />\n-萬波Wanpo Tea Shop(送飲品)<br />\n-珍心素食豆漿豆腐花專門店(送野食)<br />\n-Little Fresh Caf&eacute; &am